Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Recently underwent an extensive lobby renovation, replacement of the HVAC chillers, modernization of the elevator system and renovations to the common corridors and restrooms.
1650 Arch is Gold LEED Certified existing, BOMA Performance 360 winner, and Energy Star rated.
Great location in proximity to various retail amenities, City Hall, SEPTA and Suburban Station, and the Comcast Hub and associated retail amenities.

Newly created 5-Star amenity center available for Tenant use located on the 21st floor, the amenity center offers a conference room/training center for up to 80 people. The conference center includes a kitchen, and several breakout areas as well.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: 1650 Arch Street is located in the heart of Center City, in proximity to various retail amenities, City Hall, SEPTA and Suburban Station, and the Comcast Hub and associated retail amenities.
